25
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:45,960
Dad.

26
00:01:47,210 --> 00:01:48,050
Dad.

27
00:01:50,360 --> 00:01:51,200
Kid,

28
00:01:51,590 --> 00:01:54,160
I have to protect the abode.

29
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:56,190
This is the punishment for me.

30
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:57,640
Hurry up.

31
