Hurry. Leave now.

32
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:01,230
I can't control myself anymore.

33
00:02:01,590 --> 00:02:02,430
Quick!

34
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:13,840
Heavenly Flames

35
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:17,080
are devoured by Nihility Devouring Flame.

36
00:02:22,360 --> 00:02:23,470
Sky Mansion Alliance,

37
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:24,880
tiny as an ant.

38
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:30,440
Dad.

39
00:02:32,190 --> 00:02:33,030
Dad.

40
00:02:33,670 --> 00:02:34,510
Dad.

41
00:02:37,540 --> 00:02:39,430
Do you know how long
I've been searching for you?

42
00:02:41,440 --> 00:02:43,470
I thought you had been dead.

43
00:02:47,630 --> 00:02:50,670
I fought with Purifying Lotus Demon Saint.

44
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,600
At last, I was defeated.

45
00:02:53,670 --> 00:02:55,440
To get rid of him,

46
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:58,670
I had to leave Demon Core behind.

47
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:06,000
Dad,

48
00:03:06,750 --> 00:03:07,590
look.

49
00:03:08,390 --> 00:03:09,830
I live up to your expectations.

50
00:03:11,470 --> 00:03:13,600
My bloodline of
the Ancient Dragon of Taixu awoke.

51
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:16,270
I'm now the matriarch.

52
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,720
You've grown up.

53
00:04:00,830 --> 00:04:01,670
It looks like

54
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,360
he has obtained God Fledgling Pill.

55
00:04:04,390 --> 00:04:06,000
Devouring Spirit Eliminating Life Formation.

56
00:04:07,670 --> 00:04:09,830
It can suck all creatures into it,

57
00:04:09,830 --> 00:04:10,830
crush them with force,

58
00:04:11,110 --> 00:04:11,950
and absorb their energy.

59
00:04:14,390 --> 00:04:15,440
How brutal.

60
00:04:16,350 --> 00:04:18,200
He's turning the world into his cauldron,

61
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:19,990
all lives into his raw material,

62
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,760
spirit of soul into his fire,

63
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:23,720
and fleshes into his pill.

64
00:04:26,070 --> 00:04:28,640
He can gather Dou Qi in a short time

65
00:04:29,320 --> 00:04:31,390
and refine the real God Pill.

66
00:04:34,270 --> 00:04:35,110
There's no way

67
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:37,550
of stopping him anymore.

68
00:04:43,230 --> 00:04:44,070
Mr. Yao?

69
00:04:44,640 --> 00:04:45,950
Is there not anything that could be done?

70
00:04:47,230 --> 00:04:49,000
I've experienced death once.

71
00:04:50,110 --> 00:04:51,270
There's nothing to be afraid of.

72
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,830
At the worst, the world becomes my grave.

73
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:55,640
A pleasure for me.

74
00:05:00,160 --> 00:05:01,720
When the God Pill is refined,

75
00:05:02,270 --> 00:05:04,880
I, Huntian Emperor, will become the God.

76
00:05:06,270 --> 00:05:08,200
Anyone willing to follow the Hall of Souls

77
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:10,880
can share the world with me.

78
00:05:11,950 --> 00:05:13,510
Don't blame me for my ruthlessness

79
00:05:14,270 --> 00:05:16,110
if you are unwilling.

80
00:05:37,550 --> 00:05:38,390
Dou God.

81
00:05:39,160 --> 00:05:40,000
Ancient jade.

82
00:05:41,040 --> 00:05:42,000
Treasure.

83
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,600
Treasure.

84
00:05:43,830 --> 00:05:44,670
Dad.

85
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,560
Mr. Dragon Emperor,

86
00:05:47,830 --> 00:05:48,720
what are you…

87
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:51,550
What Dragon Emperor.

88
00:05:51,790 --> 00:05:53,720
I'm not Dragon Emperor.

89
00:05:53,920 --> 00:05:56,350
I'm not worth the title, either.

90
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:58,440
I didn't get Core Qi,

91
00:05:58,640 --> 00:06:00,760
nor did I save Dragon Tribe.

92
00:06:00,760 --> 00:06:03,320
What kind of Dragon Emperor am I?

93
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,320
Dad,

94
00:06:05,440 --> 00:06:06,600
are you confused?

95
00:06:07,070 --> 00:06:08,390
What Core Qi?

96
00:06:10,230 --> 00:06:11,070
Core Qi

97
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:13,480
is the power supporting the world,

98
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,640
the lifeblood.

99
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:17,160
Core Qi,

100
00:06:17,640 --> 00:06:19,320
the power supporting the world?

101
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,200
Tuoshe Ancient Emperor was a villain.

102
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:25,200
Why did he put God Fledgling Pill here

103
00:06:25,440 --> 00:06:27,160
if he didn't want it to be snatched?

104
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:30,280
That's it!

105
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:32,560
Ancient Emperor's treasure

106
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:33,720
is not God Fledgling Pill.

107
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:35,560
Mr. Dragon Emperor,

108
00:06:35,790 --> 00:06:37,350
where's the Core Qi?

109
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:38,670
Core Qi…

110
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,550
Core Qi…

111
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,440
Xiao Yan,

112
00:06:41,670 --> 00:06:43,230
before Senior Xiao Xuan died,

113
00:06:43,550 --> 00:06:44,390
he once said

114
00:06:45,070 --> 00:06:47,320
Source of Power
underpinned the Dou Qi Continent.

115
00:06:47,830 --> 00:06:49,640
The reason why there were
no more new Dou Gods

116
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:50,830
was because of it.

117
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:53,640
Could the Source of Power he mentioned

118
00:06:54,200 --> 00:06:55,200
be this Core Qi?

119
00:06:58,110 --> 00:06:59,440
Is there any Core Qi here?

120
00:07:00,230 --> 00:07:01,440
How come I can't feel any.

121
00:07:03,830 --> 00:07:05,320
What Ancient Emperor wanted to protect

122
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,880
is not that easy to be found by others,

123
00:07:08,950 --> 00:07:10,110
even by Huntian Emperor.

124
00:07:12,390 --> 00:07:13,320
This Ancient Emperor's Abode

125
00:07:13,950 --> 00:07:15,040
must hide some secrets.

126
00:07:29,350 --> 00:07:30,880
This is the Bodhisattva Tree.

127
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:34,040
I heard they were all over Dou Qi Continent

128
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:35,200
and shared the same root.

129
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:37,320
When Hun Miesheng was sealed here,

130
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:39,600
all the trees on the Dou Qi Continent

131
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:40,720
became withered.

132
00:07:41,550 --> 00:07:42,390
Yeah.

133
00:07:42,550 --> 00:07:44,270
If we want to enter the tree

134
00:07:44,270 --> 00:07:45,440
to check the seal,

135
00:07:45,530 --> 00:07:47,070
we need to trigger the energy of the tree.

136
00:07:49,670 --> 00:07:51,790
Xiao Yan, do you still remember
the Bodhisattva Tree

137
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,200
in Death Soul Mountain Range?

138
00:07:54,070 --> 00:07:55,880
We were separated back then,

139
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:57,670
but we met each other in the tree.

140
00:07:59,350 --> 00:08:00,440
Is it possible

141
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,950
that it's also a Bodhisattva Tree?

142
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:06,920
If there's any hidden secret here,

143
00:08:07,950 --> 00:08:09,230
it can be nothing else but this tree.

144
00:08:48,590 --> 00:08:50,670
Xun'er, gather the power of Eight Clans.

145
00:08:51,230 --> 00:08:53,230
The true Dou God's treasure might be open.

146
00:08:56,960 --> 00:08:57,800
Gu Clan.

147
00:08:58,550 --> 00:08:59,790
- Yan Clan.
- Ling Clan. - Yao Clan.

148
00:09:00,230 --> 00:09:01,970
- Lei Clan.
- Shi Clan. - Hun Clan.

149
00:09:37,980 --> 00:09:39,980
(Ancient Emperor Space)

150
00:09:52,110 --> 00:09:53,470
Isn't it beautiful here?

151
00:09:59,710 --> 00:10:01,760
Are you Tuoshe Ancient Emperor?

152
00:10:03,550 --> 00:10:05,710
You've got the God Fledgling Pill.

153
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:08,350
Why are you up here then?

154
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:13,600
Senior,

155
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:16,280
the Pill was taken away by Huntian Emperor.

156
00:10:17,030 --> 00:10:18,470
You've been uninformed in this abode

157
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,280
that you're the last one

158
00:10:21,030 --> 00:10:21,910
on Dou Qi Continent

159
00:10:22,110 --> 00:10:24,030
reaching the true Dou God level.

160
00:10:25,710 --> 00:10:29,030
There emerges some ruffians
who absorb others' Dou Qi

161
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,470
to improve themselves.

162
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,940
Huntian Emperor, Master of Hall of Souls,

163
00:10:33,350 --> 00:10:35,350
attempts to become a Dou God

164
00:10:35,880 --> 00:10:36,840
by refining God Pill

165
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:39,200
at the cost of all lives on Dou Qi Continent.

166
00:10:40,150 --> 00:10:41,640
With the power of Eight Clans,

167
00:10:42,840 --> 00:10:44,080
I come here, to stop him.

168
00:10:45,440 --> 00:10:46,280
So,

169
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:48,790
are you asking for the second pill from me?

170
00:10:49,230 --> 00:10:51,880
Even if there's one, you can't refine it.

171
00:10:52,350 --> 00:10:53,190
Senior,

172
00:10:53,550 --> 00:10:55,440
you broke the key of this abode into eight

173
00:10:55,670 --> 00:10:56,640
protected by Eight Clans

174
00:10:57,440 --> 00:10:59,230
to get them into cooperation

175
00:10:59,290 --> 00:11:00,590
and against the tendency of greed.

176
00:11:02,350 --> 00:11:04,110
I know the treasure in this abode

177
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:06,200
is not the Pill at all,

178
00:11:07,350 --> 00:11:09,110
but what you're truly protecting.

179
00:11:09,710 --> 00:11:10,550
Go ahead.

180
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:13,200
My ancestor once told me

181
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:16,640
the power on the Dou Qi Continent was weak

182
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,960
due to the lack of one thing.

183
00:11:20,710 --> 00:11:22,880
Your ancestor was indeed extraordinary

184
00:11:23,960 --> 00:11:25,960
for having come to this realization.

185
00:11:35,350 --> 00:11:37,670
People regard God Fledgling Pill

186
00:11:37,670 --> 00:11:38,670
as the treasure,

187
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:40,470
but they don't know

188
00:11:41,550 --> 00:11:42,790
the real treasure

189
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:45,470
is the nearly extinct Core Qi.

190
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:49,200
I call it "Core Power".

191
00:12:10,710 --> 00:12:12,230
In ancient times,

192
00:12:12,760 --> 00:12:13,880
Core Power

193
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:17,640
was born as a magic energy of nature.

194
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,640
Dou Practitioners

195
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,710
must absorb enough Core Power

196
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:24,640
to break the barrier of becoming Dou Gods.

197
00:12:25,640 --> 00:12:27,280
Dou Qi Continent, at that time,

198
00:12:27,550 --> 00:12:29,000
was in no shortage of Core Power.

199
00:12:29,470 --> 00:12:31,030
It was commonly found,

200
00:12:32,030 --> 00:12:33,710
but it was not renewable.

201
00:12:34,710 --> 00:12:35,590
That's to say,

202
00:12:37,320 --> 00:12:38,520
the more it was consumed,

203
00:12:38,790 --> 00:12:39,880
the less its reserves

204
00:12:40,400 --> 00:12:41,760
in this world.

205
00:12:46,470 --> 00:12:47,710
Dou God

206
00:12:47,790 --> 00:12:50,110
is the goal of everyone
on the Dou Qi Continent

207
00:12:50,550 --> 00:12:53,320
and the supreme existence in this world.

208
00:12:54,350 --> 00:12:55,760
When there was a new Dou God,

209
00:12:56,910 --> 00:12:59,280
there was a lot of consumption of Core Power.

210
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:02,470
It finally reached its end.

211
00:13:04,280 --> 00:13:05,760
On the Dou Qi Continent,

212
00:13:06,230 --> 00:13:08,470
Core Power has been exhausted.

213
00:13:09,670 --> 00:13:10,510
So,

214
00:13:11,150 --> 00:13:12,840
there are no more Dou Gods.

215
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:19,150
Core Power

216
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:22,640
has indeed been depleted

217
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:24,320
by ancient powerhouses.

218
00:13:25,790 --> 00:13:27,760
But what you're doing now

219
00:13:28,230 --> 00:13:29,840
is the same as what we did.

220
00:13:32,230 --> 00:13:33,760
The desire for power

221
00:13:34,790 --> 00:13:35,840
seems to be sowed

222
00:13:36,400 --> 00:13:37,640
in our hearts since we were born.

223
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,760
After I became a Dou God,

224
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:14,440
people wanted power more than ever

225
00:14:15,030 --> 00:14:17,080
and started to vie for Core Power.

226
00:14:18,230 --> 00:14:19,080
I knew clearly

227
00:14:19,590 --> 00:14:21,520
that I should be responsible.

228
00:14:22,550 --> 00:14:24,200
So, I hold the hope

229
00:14:24,470 --> 00:14:27,030
to protect the remaining Core Power

230
00:14:28,470 --> 00:14:31,400
and restore the old Dou Qi Continent.

231
00:14:39,640 --> 00:14:40,790
Inside the Bodhisattva Tree

232
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:43,110
lies the last bit of Core Power,

233
00:14:43,910 --> 00:14:46,280
the real treasure I want to protect.

234
00:14:48,590 --> 00:14:49,430
Senior,

235
00:14:50,030 --> 00:14:50,960
you nurture Core Power

236
00:14:51,230 --> 00:14:52,200
with your own power.

237
00:14:53,230 --> 00:14:54,110
Then, why did you

238
00:14:54,470 --> 00:14:55,960
make God Fledgling Pill?

239
00:15:00,000 --> 00:15:01,640
The God Fledgling Pill you saw

240
00:15:02,030 --> 00:15:03,470
was not made by me.

241
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:07,520
It was my strong desire for power.

242
00:15:09,000 --> 00:15:10,230
Over the past years,

243
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:13,470
it has been integrated with and refined by

244
00:15:13,470 --> 00:15:14,910
the 22 Heavenly Flames in the abode.

245
00:15:17,000 --> 00:15:19,280
God Fledgling Pill may help one person.

246
00:15:20,230 --> 00:15:21,350
Core Power

247
00:15:22,710 --> 00:15:24,230
can help everyone.

248
00:15:27,550 --> 00:15:28,710
You actually once owned

249
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:30,280
all the 22 Heavenly Flames.

250
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:33,520
Why

251
00:15:33,910 --> 00:15:35,590
is the first flame not there?

252
00:15:36,910 --> 00:15:39,710
Do you know the name of the first flame?

253
00:15:42,030 --> 00:15:42,870
Emperor Flame.

254
00:15:46,230 --> 00:15:49,000
It was my original name before.

255
00:15:50,840 --> 00:15:52,760
I don't own the Heavenly Flames.

256
00:15:53,150 --> 00:15:55,760
Rather, I'm shaped by them.

257
00:15:56,880 --> 00:15:59,320
A combination would produce new flames.

258
00:15:59,840 --> 00:16:00,680
As for this fact,

259
00:16:00,880 --> 00:16:02,200
you should be very clear.

260
00:16:06,840 --> 00:16:07,680
Senior,

261
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:08,910
are you referring to Xiao Yi?

262
00:16:11,520 --> 00:16:13,960
I've answered all your questions.

263
00:16:14,320 --> 00:16:16,150
You can leave now.

264
00:16:19,230 --> 00:16:20,070
Senior,

265
00:16:21,030 --> 00:16:22,400
in order to protect Core Power,

266
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:24,280
you'd like to sacrifice yourself.

267
00:16:25,110 --> 00:16:25,950
Do you want

268
00:16:25,960 --> 00:16:27,840
to see the disaster sweep
across the Dou Qi Continent?

269
00:16:28,280 --> 00:16:30,080
Huntian Emperor won't give up easily.

270
00:16:31,080 --> 00:16:32,520
What you've been protecting for years

271
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,440
will be in his hands at last.

272
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:37,670
You're indeed smart,

273
00:16:39,440 --> 00:16:41,910
but you're a human after all.

274
00:16:42,520 --> 00:16:43,520
Just give up.

275
00:16:45,590 --> 00:16:46,430
Senior,

276
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,030
Xiao Xuan, my ancestor,

277
00:16:52,440 --> 00:16:54,110
sacrificed the power of bloodline of Xiao Clan

278
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:56,280
to put Huntian Emperor under seal,

279
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:57,760
bringing centuries of peace to the world.

280
00:16:59,880 --> 00:17:01,150
Nowadays, in Xiao Clan,

281
00:17:01,880 --> 00:17:03,880
I'm the only one with the power of bloodline.

282
00:17:05,830 --> 00:17:08,480
I'm more than willing to sacrifice everything.

283
00:17:10,000 --> 00:17:11,830
You tried everything you could

